2. In this Act, unless the context otherwise requires-              g’;peb-
    “Authority” means the River Rafting Authority estab-
         lished by section 3;
    “fund”means the fund mentioned in section 6;
    “raft” includes a boat or other vessel;
    “raftsman” means the person who steers a river raft or
         propels it manually;
    “river raft” means a raft used or to be used for carry-
         ing passengers for reward on a river, not being a
         prescribed boat or vessel;
    “river rafting” and “rafting” mean the use of any raft
         as a river raft.
